OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FThe CrowdStrike outage ` which caused
OL,7,Fmassive disruption in the NHS,
OL,8,Ftransport, banking and wider
OL,9,Finfrastructure ` means the state of
OL,10,Fglobal IT supply chains became one of
OL,11,Fthe big tech talking points of 2024.
OL,13,FThe unlikely talking point came to the
OL,14,Fpublic's attention in July, when a far-
OL,15,Freaching global IT outage saw
OL,16,Ftransport links shut down, parts of
OL,17,Fthe NHS revert to pen and paper, and
OL,18,Feven TV broadcasters unable to get on
OL,19,Fthe air.
