OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FIt soon emerged the issue was a defect
OL,7,Fin a software update for Microsoft
OL,8,FWindows users from cybersecurity firm
OL,9,FCrowdStrike, with the flaw knocking
OL,10,Fsystems offline.
OL,12,FThe widespread nature of the issue was
OL,13,Fastonishing ` transport hubs around
OL,14,Fthe world went offline, as did systems
OL,15,Flinked to online banking, healthcare
OL,16,Fand media organisations.
