OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FOnce it was established that the
OL,7,Fincident was not security-related or a
OL,8,Fcyber attack, attention quickly turned
OL,9,Fto just how vulnerable global IT
OL,10,Fsystems were to widespread problems
OL,11,Fsuch as this, with many experts
OL,12,Fwarning that one of the root causes
OL,13,Fwas an over-reliance on small numbers
OL,14,Fof firms for IT systems.
OL,16,FThey argued that this meant that a
OL,17,Fsingle issue with one provider, in
OL,18,Fthis case CrowdStrike, meant millions
OL,19,Fof computers around the world could be
OL,20,Fknocked offline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
