OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FAt the time of the outage, experts
OL,7,Fsuggested there was an element of
OL,8,Fbusinesses sticking with what they
OL,9,Fknow in using operating systems such
OL,10,Fas Microsoft's Windows, and also
OL,11,Fconcerns about the cost of training
OL,12,Fstaff to use a new and different
OL,13,Fsystem could be part of the issue.
OL,15,FIndustry expert Dafydd Vaughan, chief
OL,16,Ftechnology officer at consultancy
OL,17,FPublic Digital, said the Government
OL,18,Fneeded to do more to boost competition
OL,19,Fwithin supply chains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
