OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FTaking the example of the NHS, which
OL,7,Fwas badly impacted by the CrowdStrike
OL,8,Foutage, he said: "EMIS ` a major
OL,9,Fprovider of services to GP surgeries,
OL,10,Fhandling health records, appointment
OL,11,Fbookings and more ` is used in more
OL,12,Fthan 60% of GP surgeries in England
OL,13,Fand Wales.
OL,15,F"The Government needs to consider the
OL,16,Frisk that comes with so few companies
OL,17,Fcontrolling so much of our essential
OL,18,Finfrastructure.
