OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,F"In all industries, Government should
OL,7,Fsee the value of more competition in
OL,8,Ftheir supply chains, and work to
OL,9,Fincrease the number of companies that
OL,10,Fprovide these essential services and
OL,11,Favoid monopolies controlling our
OL,12,Fnational infrastructure."
OL,14,FThat specific issue could be something
OL,15,Fraised in 2025, but in the meantime,
OL,16,Fthe Government has already taken steps
OL,17,Fto boost the protection around IT
OL,18,Finfrastructure by announcing the
OL,19,Fdesignation of data centres as
OL,20,Fcritical national infrastructure (CNI).
