OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FThis means data centres are now on the
OL,7,Fsame footing as vital utilities such
OL,8,Fas energy and water, and therefore
OL,9,Freceive additional support should a
OL,10,Fmajor incident affecting them occur.
OL,12,FThis decision comes in a year where
OL,13,Fanother wave of notable outages `
OL,14,Fbeyond just CrowdStrike occurred `
OL,15,Fincluding a number of repeated issues
OL,16,Fand outages linked with banking apps
OL,17,Fin the UK, other Microsoft server
OL,18,Fissues, social media platform glitches
OL,19,Fand others.
