OL,3,CHow the CrowdStrike outage made IT
OL,4,Csupply chains the new big issue in tech
OL,6,FAfter coming to power in July, the
OL,7,FLabour Government said it would
OL,8,Fintroduce the Cyber Security and
OL,9,FResilience Bill, which would give
OL,10,Fgreater power to regulators to push
OL,11,Fmore firms to implement better
OL,12,Fcybersecurity defences by expanding
OL,13,Fthe remit of existing regulation and
OL,14,Fput regulators on a stronger footing,
OL,15,Fas well as increasing the reporting
OL,16,Frequirements placed on businesses to
OL,17,Fhelp build a better picture of cyber
OL,18,Fthreats to the UK.
OL,20,FThat Bill is set to be introduced to
OL,21,FParliament in 2025.
